item.title: CVE-2018-15332|2024-08-05T09:54:02.334Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- big-ip%20%28apm%29%2C%20big-ip%20apm%20clients%2C%20big-ip%20edge%20client
item.description: The svpn component of the F5 BIG-IP APM client prior to version 7.1.7.2 for Linux and macOS runs as a privileged process and can allow an unprivileged user to get ownership of files owned by root on the local client host in a race condition.
